dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"基本調理: 戒凍野，煲八珍湯。無效再試西醫。<br />\n婦科一次千鬆啲，首先會開避孕藥試下調經，仲係痛就再照下超聲波<br />\n<br />\n利申: 老婆試過"},{"pid":"e7eb5e0cca61b65ce72ff005a7e1d0e37dd91bfc","tid":2258753,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"咁又係開上痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b056d85da73ded92d1cf51741aa7aa66b625bd35","tid":2258753,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"唔係m痛 做愛無舒緩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fd281cd17986f388626799a0312fcad9003494","tid":2258753,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"係咪唔會戒口 成日食生冷嘢飲凍嘢"},{"pid":"70b1226c90c083cf9af8387c854a072149638abc","tid":2258753,"uid":225102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥好似有用"},{"pid":"7d792afadb173c668ad2dc3e4fdc5b227f4df6cb","tid":2258753,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"每次痛來幾耐痛幾耐定只last一兩日？<br />\n經量多唔多？<br />\n顏色有冇異常？<br />\n經期間有冇其他不適，比如頭暈噁心？<br />\n來經以外既日子有冇特別比如分泌物異常？<br />\n<br />\n如果上述答案皆後者，咁就多數無乜大礙，唔放心就去照照抽個血囉，但你預都係排除大野確保唔係大問題比如cancer之類，然後開d pain killer比你咁，原則上普通m痛可以試下食nsaid比如ibuprofen ，好過坊間普通既止痛藥效，好多醫生m痛都係食nsiad就算，記得nsaid會傷胃，最好配返胃藥來食"},{"pid":"03b270527bb626aa5214472d8962dd352a4f2033","tid":2258753,"uid":361462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"子宮內膜異位可以令m痛痛得好勁<br />\n之前見有子宮內膜異位檢查計劃，合資格可以有資助做盆腔超聲波檢查，唔知而家仲有無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=692632091516190&amp;id=174953659950705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D692632091516190%26id%3D174953659950705&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=9d0d36f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=692632091516190&amp;id=174953659950705</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e925a13015c7c9cb15949e4d27a5a0651e1af4","tid":2258753,"uid":45891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"我以前會痛到起唔到身/個肚完全冇力<br />\n有次出街暈低就睇婦產科照子宮<br />\n原來生咗幾粒瘜肉所以嚟m又痛量又多<br />\n成因之一係吸收太多雌激素<br />\n即係食補品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />燕窩桃膠白鳳丸嗰啲<br />\n做手術切走瘜肉之後好好多<br />\n終於唔再驚嚟m啦"},{"pid":"78d05cd73dc8c77019f9b00eca0a580eb82f5349","tid":2258753,"uid":141736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de12809c91d70d6bb9fc98d0b2de4385f5efabdd","tid":2258753,"uid":380158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"每個月黎M都一定痛到仆街<br />\n係痛到之前返工返學黎一兩日都要請假<br />\n有睇過中醫<br />\n食過一排中藥覺得冇咩分別都係痛得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次決定去睇下婦科好啲 驚係個子宮有事<br />\n想問有冇好嘅婦科醫生介紹同埋睇一次大概要幾錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"真係建議去睇，唔好拖，有咩事都係自己辛苦，但未有時間去睇之前可以試下用暖貼暖下肚，因為好多時女仔m痛除左係內膜移位之外就係血氣唔好，所以可以試下用下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7a7821cdb64071b16d38b0dd4a3f63f85d4ef0","tid":2258753,"uid":141736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"同埋真係想講，好多女仔覺得痛就去忍，個個女仔來m都痛架啦呢d咁撚錯既觀念，真係唔好慳埋啲無謂錢，有病就去睇醫生"},{"pid":"1434dc68c142e49bcc61b23172bd3772f7303944","tid":2258753,"uid":96008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:21:37.000Z","msg":"不如試下每日都暖水浸腳"},{"pid":"f1f0a9cc42e232b05544c77643488a4adf0695ed","tid":2258753,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"花幾百一千蚊直接睇一次婦科<br />\n照超聲波就知有冇事<br />\n如果冇事直接去搵中醫調理<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n第一次照發現有朱古力瘤，即刻喺私院做手術，好彩自己有買保險"},{"pid":"cd8a72d2099ac8955eecf940837bd892ebe3a389","tid":2258753,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVaTW1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVaTW1y.png&h=698778ed&s={SIZE}\" />每個月嚟完後飲會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平平地試下 ， 好多人話有用"},{"pid":"385277317660004f493e78d4ecf90d0cac53ac3e","tid":2258753,"uid":70790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebb6582484aac70cd0262f33658849b45c75e33","tid":2258753,"uid":70790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"385277317660004f493e78d4ecf90d0cac53ac3e","tid":2258753,"uid":70790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c7e1ac3aaba5e8a51f85065b82b7c0b4338710","tid":2258753,"uid":245549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"我去家計會叫佢地幫我轉介去照，照完拎報告翻家計會睇<br />\n<br />\n150蚊家計會加照660蚊加150家計會，都係960"},{"pid":"c07fe83fd0a0e22cc30dd9ca8a363d69a9c28f20","tid":2258753,"uid":253373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote